<section class="rbp-post-checkout">
  <div class="page-width rbp-post-checkout__hero">
    <p class="rbp-post-checkout__eyebrow">Next step after checkout</p>
    <h1>Complete your Core Service intake</h1>
    <p>Select the Core Service you purchased and complete the matching intake form. Use the same email address and order number from your Shopify order confirmation.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="page-width rbp-post-checkout__grid">
    <a class="rbp-post-checkout__card" href="/pages/business-health-check-intake"><span>$250</span><h2>Business Health Check Intake</h2><p>For diagnostic review and recommended next steps.</p></a>
    <a class="rbp-post-checkout__card" href="/pages/business-advisor-intake"><span>$250</span><h2>Business Advisor Intake</h2><p>For practical advice and recommended actions.</p></a>
    <a class="rbp-post-checkout__card" href="/pages/decision-desk-intake"><span>$450</span><h2>Decision Desk Intake</h2><p>For structured business decision support.</p></a>
    <a class="rbp-post-checkout__card" href="/pages/risk-advisor-intake"><span>$550</span><h2>Risk Advisor Intake</h2><p>For exposure review and mitigation direction.</p></a>
    <a class="rbp-post-checkout__card" href="/pages/the-fixer-intake"><span>$0 quote intake</span><h2>The Fixer Intake</h2><p>For scoping a defined business problem.</p></a>
  </div>
  <div class="page-width rbp-post-checkout__note">
    <strong>Order number required:</strong> Your intake form asks for your Shopify order number so Remote Business Partner can match your submission to your purchase.
  </div>
</section>
<style>
.rbp-post-checkout{padding:48px 0 72px}.rbp-post-checkout__hero{padding:42px 30px;border-radius:28px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(var(--color-foreground),.06),rgba(var(--color-button),.08));border:1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground),.08)}.rbp-post-checkout__eyebrow{text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.13em;font-size:1.2rem;color:rgba(var(--color-foreground),.68);margin:0 0 12px}.rbp-post-checkout h1{font-size:clamp(3rem,5vw,5.8rem);line-height:1.02;margin:0}.rbp-post-checkout__hero p{max-width:780px;font-size:1.7rem;color:rgba(var(--color-foreground),.76)}.rbp-post-checkout__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,minmax(0,1fr));gap:16px;margin-top:24px}.rbp-post-checkout__card{display:block;text-decoration:none;color:rgb(var(--color-foreground));padding:24px;border-radius:24px;border:1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground),.1);background:rgb(var(--color-background));box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.04)}.rbp-post-checkout__card span{font-weight:700;color:rgba(var(--color-foreground),.7)}.rbp-post-checkout__card h2{font-size:2rem;margin:10px 0}.rbp-post-checkout__card p{color:rgba(var(--color-foreground),.72)}.rbp-post-checkout__note{margin-top:22px;padding:18px 22px;border-radius:18px;background:rgba(var(--color-foreground),.04);border:1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground),.08)}@media(max-width:990px){.rbp-post-checkout__grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}@media(max-width:749px){.rbp-post-checkout__grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.rbp-post-checkout__hero{padding:28px 20px}}
</style>
